List of known bugs and limitations:

  - Putting spaces in a chained variable or expression assignment causes errors (a  = b  = c   =  2  )
  - Errors while assigning variables go completely crazy (a=1/0 gives you random error positions)

List of "bugs" which are not to be fixed:

  - Putting two variables together doesn't multiply them (x=2; y=3; xy isn't 6)
  -
